/**
   \mainpage

   \section Installation

   System specific settings for compilers and libraries are defined in Makefile.inc

   Call <tt>make</tt> to compile everything.

   Call <tt>make install</tt> to install binaries. 
   Environment variable <tt>FMD</tt> defines installation directory.

   Call <tt>make doc</tt> to create html documentation from source.

   \section Example Usage

   The mentioned files can be found in the <tt>exmaples</tt> directory.

   

*/